      "patchset_number": 6,
      "line": 38,
      "message": "for me it is a little bit confusing, it cannot be null when you assign certificate in constructor, but  when certificate is loading null is accepted, if that logic is required for information purpose you can add a comment about it",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 6931,
